wiki.summary: “Girl Of My Dreams” is a posthumously released track by Chicago native, Juice WRLD. In this track, Juice raps about his love and affection for his significant other, touching on the deepest feelings in his respective relationship. In July 2021, the track was previewed on Instagram by Lil Bibby, a co-founder of Juice’s label, Grade A Productions. Towards the end of 2021, information leaked from one of the producers that the track would be released on Juice's second posthumous album, "Fighting Demons". Read more on Last.fm.
